                                    About SUpost
                                </h2>
                                <p class="mt-1 small text-secondary px-auto text-justify">
                                     Welcome to SUpost. I built SUpost to enable Stanford students and staff to buy and sell their stuff. 
                                      SUpost requires an @stanford.edu email in order to post. So, you can be sure that all items posted on SUpost are from people affiliated with Stanford. 
                                      (The only exception to this email restriction is in the off-campus jobs section, in which anyone can post a job for a fee -- to help us cover the costs of operation.)</p>
                                        <p class="mt-1 small text-secondary px-auto text-justify">SUpost is the #1 marketplace at Stanford! SUpost gets over 1,000,000 page views per month from Stanford students, alumni, staff and faculty. 
                                      Need to find housing? Check out the SUpost housing listings. Got something to sell? Post it! Looking to sublet your apartment? Post it! Need a bike for your ride to class through campus? Post it! Post it! 
                                      Tell everyone you know at Stanford to post one item they want to sell on SUpost, and watch this site continue to be an incredibly useful resource at Stanford.
                                </p>
                                <p class="mt-1 small text-secondary">
                                        - Greg Wientjes
                                    </p>
