    <section>
        <div class="container pb-5 pt-5 pl-5">
            <div class="row justify-content-center text-center mb-5">
                <div class="col-10">
                    <h1 class="h1 heading position-relative d-inline-block line mb-5">Why SUpost?</h1>
                    <p>I started about this idea way back in 2009, <i>"What if we have some place where people could start selling their stuff"</i>. The internet was not much of a thing back then as it was just new, for some it's a new place to explore and have fun, a new way to communicate to people far away. I know it would be a perfect place to start so I began researching on how to make it possible.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-4">
                    <span class="fas fa-user-shield fa-3x mb-4 text-info"></span>
                    <h4 class="h4 mb-2 text-success">Security</h4>
                            <p>Listings here are only posted by stanford affiliated email.</p>
                            <p>Your credentials will never be used or sold to third-party advertisers.</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-4">
                    <span class="fas fa-universal-access fa-3x mb-4 text-info"></span>
                    <h4 class="h4 mb-2 text-success">Accessibility</h4>
                         <p>Can be accessed on any devices that can browse through the internet. No app installation needed.</p>
                         <p>The new layout is easy to navigate and very intuitive, you won't get lost finding what you are looking for!</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="col-12 col-md-4 p-4">
                    <span class="fas fa-bell fa-3x mb-4 text-info"></span>
                    <h4 class="h4 mb-2 text-success">Up to date</h4>
                        <p>Listings are updated real time.</p>
                        <p>Get notified immediately on your post or request when somebody sends you a message.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <hr class="mr-5 ml-5 pb-5">
